org.opengrok.indexer.analysis

Class PathlikeMatchedEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opengrok.indexer.analysis.PathlikeMatchedEvent

  • public class PathlikeMatchedEvent
extends Object
    Represents an event raised when a symbol matcher matches a path-like string that would not be published as a symbol.
